channel.title: 614 server/client Updated And fixed No more errors!
channel.description:
Ok so After Some time i finerly Fixed the errors evry one was having And thort i would get this up as fast as posible To stop some flaming :P
Thing's added was compiler :eek:
New cache From an unkown source :|
And some Bug fix's With the server And client {i could not get rid off the warning's when compileing the client but still work's :) }
Ok so Download the new Package here...(server/client) [url=http://www.mediafire.com/?0di6injuc9ultdi]http://www.mediafire.com/?0di6injuc9ultdi[/url]
And the Cache here [url=http://www.mediafire.com/?oq540p8zozk8c9c]http://www.mediafire.com/?oq540p8zozk8c9c[/url]
Now With the cache you need To put it in you'r C:/
once in there rename it to "revengescapecache"
Then Run the source then client :)
[IMG]http://i37.tinypic.com/2ziy9l3.jpg[/img]
If you have any problem's post Below ill be sure to help.
Almost forgot 100% cred's To funky boyz krew For client and source
If anyone will please donate some rsgp to me then pm me!
